# This directory stores downloaded AI model files.
# Models are excluded from git due to their large size.
#
# Run this to download all required models:
#   python scripts/download_models.py
#
# Expected contents after download:
#   models/
#   ├── xtts/           ← XTTS-v2 model files (~1.8GB)
#   └── fish/           ← Fish Speech model files (optional)
#
# Whisper models are cached automatically by faster-whisper
# to the default HuggingFace cache directory.
